# Stray tsc emits next to convex sources. If packages/crm-api's tsconfig is
# ever accidentally run without noEmit, tsc will dump .js/.d.ts/.d.ts.map next
# to every convex/*.ts (because crm-api's src/ re-exports from ../../convex).
# Those stray files confuse `npx convex dev`'s esbuild entry-point scan.
# noEmit: true in packages/crm-api/tsconfig.json is the real fix; this block
# is a belt that contains the blast radius if the fix is ever unwound.
convex/*.js
convex/*.d.ts
convex/*.d.ts.map
convex/helpers/*.js
convex/helpers/*.d.ts
convex/helpers/*.d.ts.map
!convex/convex.config.ts
!convex/_generated/
